Package dtn.net Description

Main package for DTN connections based on JALBP library.

It contains the main classes for opening a ALBPSocket and for sending ALBPBundles over a DTN connection.

Creation date: 10/04/2019

Version:
1.0
Author:
Andrea Bisacchi
